<i>noun</i>: 매매 [매매], 거래 [거ː래] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>매매 [매매]</dt><br>
<dd>transaction</dd><br>
<dd>물건을 팔고 사는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of selling and buying things.</dd><br>
<dt>거래 [거ː래]</dt><br>
<dd>1. business; transaction; trade</dd><br>
<dd>돈이나 물건을 주고받거나 사고팖.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of exchanging, selling or buying money or goods.</dd><br>
<dd>2. mutual visiting</dd><br>
<dd>친교를 위해 오고가는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of coming and going in order to maintain social relationships.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>